DCOP/Amarok/Player
==================

This module enables an user to talk directly to an amaroK player.
It requires a dcop system.

First version.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module depends on:

	DCOP::Amarok;

